URL: https://sites.google.com/view/chao-lab-website/software/inext-4steps/
Description: iNEXT.4steps provides a simple function to create a complete analysis process
            with following four parts:
            Step1: Sample completeness profiles.
            Step2: Observed diversity values and asymptotic estimates.
            Step3: Non-asymptotic coverage-based rarefaction and extrapolation analysis.
            Step4: Evenness among species abundances.
            The output contains a summary table and figures. In addition, iNEXT.4stpes also 
            provides a function to compute estimated sample completeness and a function to compute
            observed (or estimated) evenness.
            See Chao et al. (2020) <doi:10.1111/1440-1703.12102> for more details.
